{"type": "article", "id": 6174, "title": "真空吸尘器 Air Revolve", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-13T07:40:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233836CReaO1WD6YlHqTAc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国最大的吸尘器品牌 Vax 日前推出一款真空吸尘器 Air Revolve。据 Vax 吸尘器新产品开发部负责人 James Holdgate 介绍，这款吸尘器征求了许多用户的意见，有用户向他们提出关于清洁楼梯时的不便，于是他们的开发团队设计了 Air Revolve 用来解决这一问题，整个机身采用透明塑料多方位缸体的设计，它的 360 度可操控性可以清理室内每一个角落，也可以一层一层地清洁楼梯，十分便利。定价 299.99 英镑（约合人民币 2873 元）<a href=\"http://www.vax.co.uk/airrevolve\" target=\"_blank\">，点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233833qt8b6pQILDwS2RP9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233834kdJzm7g0B4EDIYVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233834eQuSfWzPijykLbG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233834B0xuIO6dem8Da4iN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233835i1KRNs0EBcz8nC9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233835MPB6W2htkUHD8fbn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}